{"word":"γνωμονικός","slug":"γνωμονικός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γνωμονικός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γνώμων'><el>γνώμων</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>(<el>γνώμων</el> I) <i>fit to give judgment</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <i>experienced in</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(<el>γνώμων</el> II) <i>of</i> or <i>for sun-dials</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}